===Etymology===
First attested in the late 14th century. First attested in reference to an unintended pregnancy in 1932. From {{etyl|enm|en}}, from {{etyl|fro|en}} {{m|fro|accident}}, from {{etyl|la|en}} {{m|la|accidēns}}, present active participle of {{m|la|accidō||happen}}; from {{m|la|ad||to}} + {{m|la|cadō||fall}}. See {{m|en|cadence}}, {{m|en|case}}.

